        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow text-left">“I shared it with my whole team.” – Jamie R.</div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow text-left">“Loved the structure and practical approach.” – Morgan S.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECOND CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-blue-600 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Start Taking Care of Your Health Today</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">Get the free guide and start your journey to a healthier work life.</p>
      <button class="bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-amber-100 transition">Get the Free Guide</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
